<p>reports is a package that assists in writing reports and presentations by providing a frame work that brings together existing R, LaTeX/.docx and Pandoc tools.  The package is designed to be used with <a href="http://www.rstudio.com/">RStudio</a>, <a href="http://miktex.org/">MikTex</a>/<a href="http://www.tug.org/texlive/">Tex Live</a>/<a href="http://www.libreoffice.org/">LibreOffice</a>, <a href="http://yihui.name/knitr/">knitr</a>, <a href="http://www.carlboettiger.info/2012/05/30/knitcitations.html">knitcitations</a>, <a href="http://johnmacfarlane.net/pandoc/">Pandoc</a> and <a href="https://github.com/rapporter/pander">pander</a>.  The user will want to download these free programs to maximize the effectiveness of the reports package.</p>

